ActBank Act
SubjectProspectus (Federal Credit Unions) Regulations
PrecisPROSPECTUS (FEDERAL CREDIT UNIONS) REGULATIONS in order to (1) incorporate, by reference, provincial prospectus requirements and provide that an exemption from those requirements constitutes an exemption from federal prospectus requirements; (2) stipulate that a federal credit union must provide a minimum level of disclosure to the buyer of a security.
